---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<main class="px-8 py-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-mono text-neutral-100 bg-neutral-950 leading-relaxed">

  <h1 class="text-3xl mb-6">Contact · Community</h1>

  <p class="mb-6">
    The Groundative Tradition is a living field of study and practice.
    Its center is not online — yet these channels exist for those who
    wish to stand in dialogue and presence.
  </p>

  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-3">Community · Discord</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Join the official server <strong>Groundative Tradition</strong> — the
      space for open discussion, shared study, and coordination of works.
    </p>
    <a href="https://discord.gg/" 
       target="_blank" 
       class="px-5 py-2 border border-neutral-700 text-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-800 transition">
       Enter Discord · The Groundative Tradition
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl mb-3">Newsletter · The Groundative Way</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Receive essays, teachings, and reflections from XYNACT through the
      <em>Groundative Way Journal</em> — a periodic letter of presence and work.
    </p>
    <a href="https://journal.xynact.com"
       target="_blank"
       class="px-5 py-2 border border-neutral-700 text-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-800 transition">
       Subscribe to Journal
    </a>
  </section>

